  "details": "A vulnerability was found in YunaiV/zhijiantianya ruoyi-vue-pro up to 2026.04-jdk8-SNAPSHOT. The impacted element is the function generateUploadPath of the file yudao-module-infra/src/main/java/cn/iocoder/yudao/module/infra/service/file/FileServiceImpl.java of the component AppFileController File Upload Endpoint. Performing a manipulation results in path traversal. Remote exploitation of the attack is possible. The exploit has been made public and could be used. The patch is named 4ae3f6b2c9883978837638c14e3d18419819eeb0. It is recommended to apply a patch to fix this issue. This product is published by multiple vendors.",
